<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Relevé Bancaire FINORA</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; color: #334155; font-size: 13px; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .header { width: 100%; border-bottom: 2px solid #a855f7; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .logo { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .logo span { color: #a855f7; }
        .bank-info { float: right; text-align: right; font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.5; }
        .client-box { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 45%; float: right; }
        .client-box h4 { margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #0f172a; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .client-box p { margin: 5px 0; font-size: 12px; }
        .clear { clear: both; }
        .summary-box { width: 45%; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .summary-box h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 26px; color: #22c55e; }
        .summary-box p { margin: 5px 0 10px 0; font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        
        .iban-box { background: #1e293b; color: white; padding: 10px 15px; display: inline-block; border-radius: 6px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 30px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        th { background-color: #f1f5f9; color: #475569; text-align: left; padding: 12px; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1; }
        td { padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-size: 12px; }
        tr:nth-child(even) td { background-color: #f8fafc; }
        .type-achat { color: #ef4444; font-weight: 700; background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 10px; }
        .type-vente { color: #22c55e; font-weight: 700; background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1); padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 10px; }
        .footer { position: fixed; bottom: -20px; left: 0; right: 0; text-align: center; font-size: 9px; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <div class="bank-info">
            <strong>FINORA INVESTMENTS LTD.</strong><br>
            Campus Universitaire<br>
            1002 Tunis, Tunisie<br>
            N° d'Agrément: TRD-2026-991<br>
            Édité le {{ "now"|date("d/m/Y à H:i") }}
        </div>
        <div class="logo">FIN<span>ORA</span></div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:#64748b; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:2px; margin-top:5px;">RELEVÉ DE COMPTE OFFICIEL</div>
    </div>

    <div>
        <div class="client-box">
            <h4>Titulaire du Compte</h4>
            <p style="font-size:16px; font-weight:bold; color:#0f172a;">{{ user.username|upper }}</p>
            <p><strong>Email :</strong> {{ user.email }}</p>
            <p><strong>Identifiant Unique :</strong> #{{ user.id }}</p>
            <br>
            <p style="font-size:10px; color:#64748b; margin-bottom: 3px;">Votre Relevé d'Identité Bancaire (RIB)</p>
            <div class="iban-box">
                TN59 1000 2000 3000 {% if user.id < 10 %}000{{ user.id }}{% elseif user.id < 100 %}00{{ user.id }}{% else %}0{{ user.id }}{% endif %} 4567
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="summary-box">
            <p>SOLDE DE VOTRE COMPTE (WALLET)</p>
            <h3>{{ walletBalance|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} TND</h3>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 2px;">POUVOIR D'ACHAT DISPONIBLE IMMÉDIAT</p>
            <h4 style="margin:0; font-size:18px; color:#0f172a;">{{ walletBalance|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} TND</h4>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="clear"></div>

    <h3 style="color: #0f172a; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 16px;">Journal des Opérations Boursières (Historique)</h3>
    
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Date d'Exécution</th>
                <th>Sens de l'Ordre</th>
                <th>Placment Financier</th>
                <th>Taille (Qté)</th>
                <th>Montant Net (TND)</th>
                <th>Frais Finora</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {% for trx in transactions %}
                <tr>
                    <td style="color:#64748b; font-size: 11px;">{{ trx.dateTransaction|date("d/m/Y H:i") }}</td>
                    <td>
                        {% if trx.typeTransaction == 'ACHAT' %}
                            <span class="type-achat">DÉBIT (ACHAT)</span>
                        {% else %}
                            <span class="type-vente">CRÉDIT (VENTE)</span>
                        {% endif %}
                    </td>
                    <td><strong style="color: #0f172a;">{{ trx.action.symbole|default('N/A') }}</strong></td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;">{{ trx.quantite }}</td>
                    <td style="font-weight: bold; text-align: right;">
                        {% if trx.typeTransaction == 'ACHAT' %}
                            <span style="color:#ef4444;">- {{ (trx.montantTotal + trx.commission)|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }}</span>
                        {% else %}
                            <span style="color:#22c55e;">+ {{ (trx.montantTotal - trx.commission)|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }}</span>
                        {% endif %}
                    </td>
                    <td style="color:#94a3b8; text-align: right;">{{ trx.commission|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }}</td>
                </tr>
            {% else %}
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="6" style="text-align:center; padding:40px; color:#94a3b8;">
                        Aucune transaction boursière détectée sur ce portefeuille.
                    </td>
                </tr>
            {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="footer">
        FINORA INVESTMENTS LTD est régulée par les autorités des marchés financiers. S.A. au capital de 10.000.000 TND.<br>
        Document électronique généré informatiquement ce jour. Ce relevé est strictement confidentiel. En cas d'anomalie, contactez votre conseiller ou l'administrateur système.
    </div>

</body>
</html>
